---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="totonou — Focus & Reset App | Dopamine Lab TV"
  description="A focus and reset app built on the neuroscience of totonou. Cold exposure protocols, breathing contrast, recovery windows — your brain's recalibration system, made simple."
  lang="en"
  ogImage="/og/totonou.png"
>
  <div class="totonou-page">

    <div class="totonou-hero">
      <p class="totonou-eyebrow">Coming Soon</p>
      <div class="totonou-kanji-hero" aria-hidden="true">整</div>
      <h1 class="totonou-title">totonou</h1>
      <p class="totonou-subtitle">
        Focus & Reset — the app built on the neuroscience of recalibration.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="totonou-concept">
      <p class="totonou-concept-text">
        Your brain wasn't designed for constant stimulation.
        It was designed for <strong>contrast</strong> — high activation, then full recovery,
        landing somewhere better than where it started.
      </p>
      <p class="totonou-concept-text">
        Modern life eliminated the recovery half of the cycle.
        totonou gives it back.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="totonou-pillars">
      <div class="totonou-pillar">
        <span class="totonou-pillar-kanji">集</span>
        <h3 class="totonou-pillar-title">Focus</h3>
        <p class="totonou-pillar-body">Protocol-guided sessions designed around your nervous system's actual attention cycles — not arbitrary timers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="totonou-pillar">
        <span class="totonou-pillar-kanji">整</span>
        <h3 class="totonou-pillar-title">Reset</h3>
        <p class="totonou-pillar-body">Cold exposure, breathing contrast, and stillness protocols that trigger the parasympathetic rebound your dopamine baseline needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="totonou-pillar">
        <span class="totonou-pillar-kanji">間</span>
        <h3 class="totonou-pillar-title">Ma</h3>
        <p class="totonou-pillar-body">Deliberate recovery windows — not half-rest, not distraction. The structural silence that makes the rest of your day possible.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="totonou-science">
      <h2 class="totonou-section-title">The Science Behind It</h2>
      <div class="totonou-science-grid">
        <div class="totonou-science-item">
          <span class="totonou-science-num">300%</span>
          <p>Norepinephrine increase from brief cold exposure — sharpening prefrontal focus for 15–30 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="totonou-science-item">
          <span class="totonou-science-num">15–30<span style="font-size:1rem">min</span></span>
          <p>The totonou window — measurably elevated cognitive performance after a completed autonomic cycle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="totonou-science-item">
          <span class="totonou-science-num">∞</span>
          <p>The number of ways modern design exploits your dopamine system. totonou goes the other direction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="totonou-waitlist">
      <h2 class="totonou-waitlist-title">Be First to Know</h2>
      <p class="totonou-waitlist-body">
        Launch notification + the research behind every protocol.
        No noise. Just signal.
      </p>
      <a
        class="btn totonou-waitlist-btn"
        href="https://dopaminelabtv.substack.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Join the waitlist on Substack →
      </a>
      <p class="totonou-waitlist-note">Free. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="totonou-articles">
      <h2 class="totonou-section-title">Read the Science First</h2>
      <div class="totonou-article-links">
        <a href="/posts/totonou-what-your-brain-needs" class="totonou-article-link">
          <span class="totonou-article-label">Foundation</span>
          <span class="totonou-article-title">Totonou: The Japanese Word for What Your Brain Has Been Missing →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/posts/why-you-cant-focus-anymore" class="totonou-article-link">
          <span class="totonou-article-label">Context</span>
          <span class="totonou-article-title">Why You Can't Focus Anymore →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
